A yet-to-be identified man was shot dead on Monday during the #EndSARS protest at Surulere, Lagos. Other protesters were also arrested during the protest. It was learnt that police officers shot indiscriminately to disperse the protesters. The #ENDSARS protest is a campaign against police brutality, extortion and extra-judicial killings. Fellow protesters shared video of the incident on social media.   A yet-to-be identified man was shot dead on Monday during the #EndSARS protest at Surulere, Lagos. Other protesters were also arrested during the protest. It was learnt that police officers shot indiscriminately to disperse the protesters. The #ENDSARS protest is a campaign against police brutality, extortion and extra-judicial killings. Fellow protesters shared video of the incident on social media.  